{"tid":1327341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[懶人包] 點解同點樣反個人信用評分系統？","createTime":"2019-07-17T14:30:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T12:20:32.000Z","uid":123713,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"201b96abff3a0eabd23efed0e3bfe7997aec8218","tid":1327341,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:30:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咩係個人信用評分系統？</span></span></strong> 以下來自百度<br />\n<blockquote>個人信用評分系統(Credit Scoring System)是一套定量評估個人信用風險的應用系統，它通過對個人客戶信息進行量化計算得出信用分值，反映個人客戶的信用狀況。個人信用評分系統廣泛地應用於個人信貸、信用卡、保險理賠等金融業務中，為信用政策的制定、分析、評估、優化提供量化支持。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n簡單D講即係用最新科技，全方位大包圍咁收集每一個市民既個人資料，再由中共制度既「評分標準」去進去奬懲既動作。<br />\n<br />\n中國大城市已經行緊呢個信用系統，目標係數年內於全國舖設，連農村都會輻蓋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係中國已經收集緊既數據包括： <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 衣食住行數據</span></strong></span><br />\n中國mobile payment/ecommerce 既發達程度，令佢既國民生活大小事都離唔開ecommerce。<br />\n加上早年强推既實名制，令中國人所有既網絡足跡都被紀錄得一清二楚。<br />\n以下公司全部都有BAT（百度／阿里巴巴／騰訊）注資／持有包括但不限於：<br />\n生活雜貨：淘寶京東<br />\n出行旅遊：攜程、去哪兒、滴滴（早前收購埋Uber China)、共享單車<br />\n消費娛樂：大眾點評、美團<br />\n金融／支付: 理財類例如餘額寶、螞蟻金服，支付類包括交水費電費上網電話費，仲包括落樓下食雲吞麵個老闆娘都驚收假銀紙而逼你用mobile payment<br />\n<br />\n基本上生活大小事都全方面被實名制既online payment所包圍，完全走唔甩。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>關信用系統咩事？</strong></span><br />\n呢個係第一步，係人面識別Cam未成熟既時候已經佈下既天羅地網<br />\n中共要砌你生豬肉話咁易，拎住你每日每個動作既數據，是但用個理由：購買／收藏危險品、惡意負評尋釁滋事、出行去敏感地區煽動國家都可以捉你去返。可能佢唔夠證據，但可以「拘留」你半年先放你走。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 天眼錄像監控</span></strong></span><br />\n利君雅講得好清楚，直接去片。<br />\n我只highligh一句：<br />\n<blockquote>目標2020年做到全域覆蓋，全國互聯互通，3年後全國可能多達27億個人工智能天眼。</blockquote><br />\n《視點31》【新疆監控通道曝光，監控趨勢延伸本港？】（RTHK31：16/4/2019）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dh4Su3zvRDU&amp;t=95s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Ddh4Su3zvRDU%26t%3D95s&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQstagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=e251c8b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dh4Su3zvRDU&amp;t=95s</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咁對中國人有咩影響？</span></strong></span><br />\n<blockquote>就係隨時砌你老未生豬肉</blockquote><br />\n睇左中國官方宣傳片先<br />\n中國公益宣传片:失信被执行人不能干些啥?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.iqiyi.com/v_19rqylcx1g.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iqiyi.com%2Fv_19rqylcx1g.html&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQstagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=f106273f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.iqiyi.com/v_19rqylcx1g.html</a><br />\n<br />\n《诚信缙云 杜绝失信》公益宣传片<br />\n<a href=\"https://v.qq.com/x/page/u0813dx5vic.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fv.qq.com%2Fx%2Fpage%2Fu0813dx5vic.html&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQstagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=45d81dd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://v.qq.com/x/page/u0813dx5vic.html</a><br />\n<br />\n再睇埋港台： <br />\n《視點31》【黑鏡人生‧淪落失信人】（RTHK31：30/4/2019）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=srcGtNTMWvs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsrcGtNTMWvs&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQstagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=b9120948\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=srcGtNTMWvs</a><br />\n<br />\n《視點31》【中國式‧信用】（RTHK31：23/4/2019）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sPZ9gSIffjE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsPZ9gSIffjE&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQstagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=4b85457c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sPZ9gSIffjE</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咁關香港人咩事？</span></strong></span><br />\n1. 所謂智能燈柱<br />\n睇完上面中國咩情況，相信大家一定明白裝左＝白色恐怖。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但更恐怖既係已經裝撚左50支，</span></strong></span>黎緊會裝400支。而呢400支只係先導計劃，陸續有黎。<br />\n<br />\nAM730 - 20190717 - 市民憂智慧燈柱侵犯私隱 創科局暫緩識別車牌功能<br />\n<blockquote>創科局昨......宣布「暫緩」啟動部分功能，包括以全景攝影機收集車牌號碼、藍牙交通探測器測車速等，直至區議會取得共識後，才考慮重新啟動或加裝更多功能。......政府有採取私隱保障措施，包括降低燈柱內自動交通快拍的解像度，令人難以透過影像識辨人臉及車牌。</blockquote><br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e5%b8%82%e6%b0%91%e6%86%82%e6%99%ba%e6%85%a7%e7%87%88%e6%9f%b1%e4%be%b5%e7%8a%af%e7%a7%81%e9%9a%b1-%e5%89%b5%e7%a7%91%e5%b1%80%e6%9a%ab%e7%b7%a9%e8%ad%98%e5%88%a5%e8%bb%8a%e7%89%8c%e5%8a%9f%e8%83%bd-180793\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25e5%25b8%2582%25e6%25b0%2591%25e6%2586%2582%25e6%2599%25ba%25e6%2585%25a7%25e7%2587%2588%25e6%259f%25b1%25e4%25be%25b5%25e7%258a%25af%25e7%25a7%2581%25e9%259a%25b1-%25e5%2589%25b5%25e7%25a7%2591%25e5%25b1%2580%25e6%259a%25ab%25e7%25b7%25a9%25e8%25ad%2598%25e5%2588%25a5%25e8%25bb%258a%25e7%2589%258c%25e5%258a%259f%25e8%2583%25bd-180793&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQstagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=806b828d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e5%b8%82%e6%b0%91%e6%86%82%e6%99%ba%e6%85%a7%e7%87%88%e6%9f%b1%e4%be%b5%e7%8a%af%e7%a7%81%e9%9a%b1-%e5%89%b5%e7%a7%91%e5%b1%80%e6%9a%ab%e7%b7%a9%e8%ad%98%e5%88%a5%e8%bb%8a%e7%89%8c%e5%8a%9f%e8%83%bd-180793</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. Mobile payment去收集數據<br />\n近年大家都係互大連鎖餐廳／零售商都見唔少相關既燒錢優惠，目標就係想好似係中國咁，透過燒錢去培養用戶既習慣同loyalty, 到最後就獨占市場，拎撚晒大家既data。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wY1kqcR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwY1kqcR.png&h=be8154b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但事情愈演愈烈，已經滲透到去公共事務。<br />\nAM730 - 20190712 - WeChat Pay交電費有20元現金券<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/7/1562848311_J6-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F7%2F1562848311_J6-1280w.jpg&h=5b8fe56c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80/wechat-pay%E4%BA%A4%E9%9B%BB%E8%B2%BB%E6%9C%8920%E5%85%83%E7%8F%BE%E9%87%91%E5%88%B8-180178\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%258A%2580%2Fwechat-pay%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E6%259C%258920%25E5%2585%2583%25E7%258F%25BE%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%2588%25B8-180178&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQstagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=fb0a4dcf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80/wechat-pay%E4%BA%A4%E9%9B%BB%E8%B2%BB%E6%9C%8920%E5%85%83%E7%8F%BE%E9%87%91%E5%88%B8-180178</a><br />\n<br />\n3. RFID身份證 百米內可抄牌<br />\n<blockquote>RFID系統可讀取資料的範圍，取決於接收器和晶片，根據國際標準，若採用高頻率(Ultra High Frequency)系統，可讀取範圍可達10米；帶電池的「主動式RFID」讀取範圍更可達100米。但如果像八達通採用的系統，接收範圍超出1米已超出國際標準。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nApple Daily - 20150121 - 拆解RFID新身份證警可隔空抄牌！<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20150121/53355070\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20150121%2F53355070&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQstagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=e105d76b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20150121%2F53355070&h=2d0e5548\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20150121/53355070</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人可以做D咩？</span></strong></span><br />\n1. 全面抵制所有中國公司既互聯網服務，特別係online payment同淘寶<br />\n2. 保護自己，買定個防RFID既卡套／銀包<br />\n3.. 一齊出黎反對政府强推監控燈柱！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n身邊有朋友死都唔信既，fwd比佢睇下<br />\n有錯／漏／補充請隨便講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n所有野都唔係陰謀論，政府website都係晒到<br />\n<br />\n國家個人信用信息公示系統<br />\n<a href=\"http://110ga.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F110ga.net%2F&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQstagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=28fe9489\" target=\"_blank\">http://110ga.net/</a><br />\n<br />\n百度百科 － 實名制<br />\n<a href=\"https://baike.baid